{"id":187,"parent_id":186,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":187,"title":"Philippians 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Philip.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Epistle of Paul the Apostle",["br"],["span.subordinate","to the"],["br"],["span.dominant","Philippians"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","All that happened to Paul furthered the gospel causeâ€”Our conduct should be worthy of the gospel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.1","order":"03.13.001.20557"},["b","1"],"Paul and Timotheus, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"servants"],"of Jesus Christ, to all the saints in Christ Jesus which are at Philippi, with the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"bishops"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"deacons"],":"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.2","order":"03.13.001.20558"},["b","2"],"Grace",["i","be"],"unto you, and peace, from God our Father, and",["i","from"],"the Lord Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.3","order":"03.13.001.20559"},["b","3"],"I thank my God upon every remembrance of you,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.4","order":"03.13.001.20560"},["b","4"],"Always in every prayer of mine for you all making request with joy,"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.5","order":"03.13.001.20561"},["b","5"],"For your fellowship in the gospel from the first day until now;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.6","order":"03.13.001.20562"},["b","6"],"Being confident of this very thing, that he which hath begun a good work in you will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"perform"],["i","it"],"until the day of Jesus Christ:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.7","order":"03.13.001.20563"},["b","7"],"Even as it is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"meet"],"for me to think this of you all, because I have you in my heart; inasmuch as both in my bonds, and in the defence and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"confirmation"],"of the gospel, ye all are partakers of my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.8","order":"03.13.001.20564"},["b","8"],"For God is my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"record"],", how greatly I long after you all in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"bowels"],"of Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.9","order":"03.13.001.20565"},["b","9"],"And this I pray, that your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"love"],"may abound yet more and more in knowledge and",["i","in"],"all judgment;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.10","order":"03.13.001.20566"},["b","10"],"That ye may",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"approve"],"things that are excellent; that ye may be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"sincere"],"and without offence till the day of Christ;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.11","order":"03.13.001.20567"},["b","11"],"Being filled with the fruits of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"righteousness"],", which are by Jesus Christ, unto the glory and praise of God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.12","order":"03.13.001.20568"},["b","12"],"But I would ye should understand, brethren, that the things",["i","which happened"],"unto me have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"fallen out"],"rather unto the furtherance of the gospel;"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.13","order":"03.13.001.20569"},["b","13"],"So that my bonds in Christ are manifest in all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"palace"],", and in all other",["i","places;"]],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.14","order":"03.13.001.20570"},["b","14"],"And many of the brethren in the Lord, waxing confident by my bonds, are much more bold to speak the word without",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"fear"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.15","order":"03.13.001.20571"},["b","15"],"Some indeed preach Christ even of envy and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"strife"],"; and some also of good will:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.16","order":"03.13.001.20572"},["b","16"],"The one preach Christ of contention, not sincerely, supposing to add affliction to my bonds:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.17","order":"03.13.001.20573"},["b","17"],"But the other of love, knowing that I am set for the defence of the gospel."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.18","order":"03.13.001.20574"},["b","18"],"What then? notwithstanding, every way, whether in pretence, or in truth, Christ is preached; and I therein do rejoice, yea, and will rejoice."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.19","order":"03.13.001.20575"},["b","19"],"For I know that this shall turn to my salvation through your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"prayer"],", and the supply of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Spirit"],"of Jesus Christ,"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.20","order":"03.13.001.20576"},["b","20"],"According to my earnest expectation and",["i","my"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"hope"],", that in nothing I shall be ashamed, but",["i","that"],"with all boldness, as always,",["i","so"],"now also Christ shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"magnified"],"in my body, whether",["i","it be"],"by life, or by death."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.21","order":"03.13.001.20577"},["b","21"],"For to me to live",["i","is"],"Christ, and to die",["i","is"],"gain."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.22","order":"03.13.001.20578"},["b","22"],"But if I live in the flesh, this",["i","is"],"the fruit of my labour: yet what I shall choose I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"wot"],"not."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.23","order":"03.13.001.20579"},["b","23"],"For I am",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"in a strait"],"betwixt two, having a desire to depart, and to be with Christ; which is far better:"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.24","order":"03.13.001.20580"},["b","24"],"Nevertheless to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"abide"],"in the flesh",["i","is"],"more needful for you."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.25","order":"03.13.001.20581"},["b","25"],"And having this confidence, I know that I shall abide and continue with you all for your furtherance and joy of faith;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.26","order":"03.13.001.20582"},["b","26"],"That your rejoicing may be more abundant in Jesus Christ for me by my coming to you again."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.27","order":"03.13.001.20583"},["b","27"],"Only let your conversation be as it becometh the gospel of Christ: that whether I come and see you, or else be absent, I may hear of your affairs, that ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"stand fast"],"in one spirit, with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"one"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"mind"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_27d"},"striving"],"together for the faith of the gospel;"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.28","order":"03.13.001.20584"},["b","28"],"And in nothing terrified by your adversaries:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"which is"],"to them an evident token of perdition, but to you of salvation, and that of God."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.29","order":"03.13.001.20585"},["b","29"],"For unto you it is given in the behalf of Christ, not only to believe on him, but also to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"suffer"],"for his sake;"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.30","order":"03.13.001.20586"},["b","30"],"Having the same conflict which ye saw in me, and now hear",["i","to be"],"in me."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.1a","order":"03.13.001.20587"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/servant"},"TG Servant"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.1b","order":"03.13.001.20589"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bishop"},"TG Bishop"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.1c","order":"03.13.001.20591"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deacon"},"TG Deacon"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.6a","order":"03.13.001.20593"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"complete, accomplish."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.7a","order":"03.13.001.20595"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"just, right."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.7b","order":"03.13.001.20597"},["b","7b"],["span.small","GR"],"establishment, strengthening."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.7c","order":"03.13.001.20599"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.8a","order":"03.13.001.20601"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"witness."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.8b","order":"03.13.001.20603"},["b","8b"],["span.small","GR"],"affections, compassions."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.9a","order":"03.13.001.20605"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.18"},"Moses 7:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.10a","order":"03.13.001.20607"},["b","10a"],["span.small","GR"],"prove, put to the test."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.10b","order":"03.13.001.20609"},["b","10b"],["span.small","GR"],"pure, spotless."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.11a","order":"03.13.001.20611"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.12a","order":"03.13.001.20613"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"come."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.13a","order":"03.13.001.20615"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.22"},"Philip. 4:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.14a","order":"03.13.001.20617"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.74.68-75"},"Luke 1:74 (68â€“75)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/4.18.15-18"},"1Â Jn. 4:18 (15â€“18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.6.5-6"},"D&C 68:6 (5â€“6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.15a","order":"03.13.001.20619"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.19a","order":"03.13.001.20621"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/1.11"},"2Â Cor. 1:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philem/1.22"},"Philem. 1:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.19b","order":"03.13.001.20623"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-spirit-of"},"TG God, Spirit of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.20a","order":"03.13.001.20625"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.116"},"Ps. 119:116"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.20b","order":"03.13.001.20627"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/34.3.1-3"},"Ps. 34:3 (1â€“3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.22a","order":"03.13.001.20629"},["b","22a"],["span.small","GR"],"know."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.23a","order":"03.13.001.20631"},["b","23a"],["span.small","GR"],"hard-pressed to choose."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.24a","order":"03.13.001.20633"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.9.1-12"},"3Â Ne. 28:9 (1â€“12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/7.5.1-8"},"D&C 7:5 (1â€“8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.27a","order":"03.13.001.20635"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.1.1-7"},"Philip. 4:1 (1â€“7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.27b","order":"03.13.001.20637"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unity"},"TG Unity"],"."],["div",{"id":"27c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.27c","order":"03.13.001.20639"},["b","27c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mind"},"TG Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"27d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.27d","order":"03.13.001.20641"},["b","27d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/jude/1.3"},"Jude 1:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.28a","order":"03.13.001.20643"},["b","28a"],["span.small","JST"],"Philip. 1:28 â€¦",["i","who reject the gospel, which bringeth on them destruction;"],"but you",["i","who receive the gospel,"],"salvation; and that of God."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.29a","order":"03.13.001.20645"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"TG Suffering"],"."]]}
